![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b5dc0c47-f51d-4b48-a410-a8b0e7a4e0c2/ep344.jpg?format=original)

We are once again thrown into the unpredictable world of _The Umbrella Academy_ as we unravel all the twists and turns of its forth, and final season. With the apocalypse looming (again), the Hargreeves siblings are back with more family drama, time-travel chaos, and mind-bending revelations. We'll break down the key moments, explore character arcs, and discuss how this season ties everything together—or blows it all apart. Whether you're team Viktor, Klaus, or Five, this is the episode you don't want to miss as we dissect every bizarre and brilliant detail of _The Umbrella Academy's_ explosive final season!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

